  "text": "The developed compact large-signal model is embedded in the Agilent Advanced Design System software [CITATION_1] by using the symbolically-defined devices (SDD) method. The large-signal equivalent circuit topology for the C-H diamond MOSFET is shown in Fig. 11 , which ignores the effect of gate leakage and dielectric breakdown.",
